<div class="row homeLogo">
    <p><i class="fa fa-bed" aria-hidden="true"></i> Room Mates</p>
</div>
<div class="row img imgLogo">
    <p><i class="fa fa-bed" aria-hidden="true"></i> Room Mates</p>
</div>

<div class="row rowHome">
<% if (currentUser) {%> 
<div class="col-xs-6 text-center col-xs-offset-3">
<%} else {%>
<div class="col-xs-5 col-xs-offset-1 text-center">
<% }%>
<br><br>
    <h3>Tired of getting awful roommates?</h3>
    <br>
    <br>
    <p>Here at room mates, we have desgined a website to assist our users to find compatible roommates. The idea is similar to
     dating. We don't think one should spend their time at home with a roommate they don't get along with. That's where we come in.</p>
     <p><strong>Step 1.</strong> Sign up</p>
     <p><strong>Step 2.</strong> Fill out your profile</p>
     <p><strong>Step 3.</strong> Search for a roommate that fits your preferences</p>
     <p><strong>Step 4.</strong> Live happily ever after</p>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-5 text-center">
<% if (!currentUser) { %>
<div class="well homeLogin">
<h4>Don't have an account? Sign up now!</h4>
<form method="POST" action="/auth/signup">
    <div class="form-group">
        <label for="username" class="label">Username</label>
        <input type="text" name="username" class="form-control" placeholder="Create Username">
    </div>
    <div class="form-group">
        <label for="firstname" class="label">First Name</label>
        <input type="text" name="fname" class="form-control" placeholder="Type your first name">
    </div>
    <div class="form-group">
        <label for="lastname" class="label">Last Name</label>
        <input type="text" name="lname" class="form-control" placeholder="Type your last name">
    </div>
    <div class="form-group">
        <label for="email" class="label">Email</label>
        <input type="text" name="email" class="form-control" placeholder="Type your email">
    </div>
    <div class="form-group">
        <label for="password" class="label">Password</label>
        <input type="password" name="password" class="form-control" placeholder="Type your password">
    </div>
    <input type="submit" class="btnwhite">
</form>
<%}%>
</div>
</div>
</div>